msg":"拘留人士票箱入面真係拘留人士投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:15:43.000Z","msg":"用槍指住黎投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39db1a5d3bd66121874382c78094eb6613c6133c","tid":1750992,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:16:12.000Z","msg":"隔離post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三個在警署內設立的專用投票站包括分別在跑馬地、長沙灣及田心警署，開放時間與一般投票站相同。在投票日遭警方、廉政公署及海關等執法機構（懲教署除外）羈押或拘留的登記選民，將被分配在就近的警署專用投票站投票，投票過程由選舉事務處職員負責及監督。<br />\n投票結束後，選舉事務處會把從各專用投票站的選票在選票分流站按選區分類，然後轉送所屬的大點票站，與在大點票站投下的選票混合後，才予以點算，屆時選票分類過程亦會開放予公眾觀察，以確保選舉的透明度。"},{"pid":"1e0ee8e2915192b70a25a153631e88838a57cd51","tid":1750992,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d6e8411b9eb44ad0c1b91c3f404e2f3b1aae20d3","tid":1750992,"uid":271545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5929deab2fa92a7da57cc90dd6d9e8fb276cecd2","tid":1750992,"uid":254865,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:08:47.000Z","msg":"拘留人士票箱入面真係拘留人士投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:15:43.000Z","msg":"用槍指住黎投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:16:31.000Z","msg":"我都咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ab40e45aef9e3e6e012b7096a6a4727beb23b3","tid":1750992,"uid":60120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:18:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61fd99ef685c66e4fd8e9d265df3d654da41891c","tid":1750992,"uid":184985,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:21:45.000Z","msg":"警署仲黑過民賤聯喎, 你估你仲咁輕鬆投自己想投果票？"},{"pid":"259e